data.description: Are you looking to live in a community that has year round activities and the holidays are insane? Welcome to this exquisite four-bedroom, two-bathroom home where luxury and style meet! The study features custom barn doors and plantation shutters, making it a great space for an in home office. This house is equipped with 8-foot doors throughout, combined with luxury vinyl plank flooring, creating a bright and spacious atmosphere. The laundry room boasts shiplap walls and butcher block countertops, a perfect blend of function and style.  Each bedroom comes with closet built-ins, offering ample storage space and organization. The gourmet kitchen features quartz countertops, gas stove and an oversized island, great for entertaining. The spacious family room features a shiplap accent wall which provides the perfect spot for relaxation and entertainment. The owner's suite offers walk-in closets with custom built ins, automatic blinds and a tray ceiling. The ensuite features a luxurious walk-in shower with a digital control panel ensuring the perfect temperature every time you step in. Step outside to the fully fenced backyard, complete with a covered lanai and a gas hookup for grilling. An ideal space for outdoor living. You’ll have access to a zero entry community pool and a covered playground. If you’re looking to get to know your neighbors, join in one of the many activities going on. Whether you’re a book worm looking for a book club, or just want to hang out at one of the monthly wine downs. There’s something for everyone. Don't miss this opportunity to turn this house into a home!
